A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend an Act to reincorporate and provide a new charter for the City of Acworth,
2 approved February 17, 1989 (Ga. L. 1989, p. 3512), as amended, particularly by an Act
3 approved May 6, 2024 (Ga. L. 2024, p. 4039), so as to adopt by reference a certain map; to
4 repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
5 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
6 SECTION 1.
7 An Act to reincorporate and provide a new charter for the City of Acworth, approved
8 February 17, 1989 (Ga. L. 1989, p. 3512), as amended, particularly by an Act approved May
9 6, 2024 (Ga. L. 2024, p. 4039), is amended by revising subsection (a) of Section 1.11 as
10 follows:
11 "(a) The boundaries of this city shall be those existing on the effective date of this charter
12 with such alterations as may be made from time to time by local law or in a manner
13 provided by general state law. The boundaries of this city at all times shall be shown on
14 a map, a written description, or any combination thereof, to be retained permanently in the
15 office of the city clerk and to be designated, as the case may be, the 'Official Map or
16 Description of the Corporate Limits of the City of Acworth, Georgia.' Photographic, typed,
