17 or other copies of such map or description certified by the city clerk shall be admitted as
18 evidence in all courts and shall have the same force and effect as the original map or
19 description. The 'Official Map or Description of the Corporate Limits of the City of
20 Acworth, Georgia,' dated December 19, 2024, prepared by the City Clerk of the City of
21 Acworth, is adopted as the official map of the corporate limits of the City of Acworth,
22 Georgia, and the corporate boundaries of the City of Acworth, Georgia, as of January 1,
23 2025, shall be reflected on said official map, subject to amendment as set forth in this
24 charter or by local Act or in accordance with the general laws of the state."
25 SECTION 2.
26 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
